= Your Brussels Playbook: A Personal Guide to Your New Life

#info-box(title: "Welcome to Your Brussels Playbook!")[
Welcome to Brussels! The past few weeks have been a whirlwind of information, from administrative tasks to cultural nuances. It's completely normal to feel overwhelmed.

*What is this playbook?*
This is not just a summary of a course; it's a *living document* designed to be your single source of truth for your new life in Brussels. It's a personalized, custom-made guidebook that you will build and grow over time.

*Why do you need it?*
The goal is to eliminate stress and save time. Instead of searching through piles of paper or old emails, you'll have one central place for every important detail—from your National Number to the name of that amazing bakery your colleague recommended.

*How do you use it?*
Start by filling in the foundational information from your move. Then, make it a habit to add new discoveries, contacts, and tips as you experience them. This playbook will grow with you, becoming an invaluable tool for navigating the city with confidence.
]

